txt.en: Wandering lost-lights can be found along the river Gladden.\n\nYou should defeat wandering lost-lights.
You have defeated many wandering lost-lights along the river Gladden, making the Vales of Anduin safer.
Strange lights flicker in the swamps and marshes in the Vales of Anduin. Wandering lost-lights move along the river Gladden. These creatures should be defeated if the Vales are to remain safe.
Wandering lost-lights move along the river Gladden.
